						class="icon-bar"></span> <span class="icon-bar"></span> <span
						class="icon-bar"></span>
				</button>
				<a class="navbar-brand" href="../index.html">
					<div class="logo text-center">
						<img src="../assets/img/fire.png" alt=""
							style="width: 50px; height: 50px;">
